					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So, Jamcon really punched my lights out. I'm only just getting back into writing really. Slowly but surely I am getting my mojo back, and the first result of this is this here article that I've wanted to do for a short while now. Anyway, on to the credits.</p> <p>Thanks to my primary reviewer, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4022320&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1560242415" alt="RockTeethMothEyes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4022320)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rockteethmotheyes" >RockTeethMothEyes</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1560242415" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span> who gave some much needed crit to the first version of this draft. Also thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/margssentif" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3861605&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1560242415" alt="margssentif" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3861605)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/margssentif" >margssentif</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athosnetwork" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5012224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1560242415" alt="AthosNetwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5012224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/athosnetwork" >AthosNetwork</a></span>, the latter of whom pointed out some glaring logical flaws that needed patching.</p> <p>Think that's all for now, hope you enjoyed the read!</p> <p>And somebody get me that suit&#8230;</p> 
